                <p>
                    The product was originally created as <strong>HelloGrade</strong>, a grading portal focused on helping schools and teachers manage grade-related workflows more clearly.
                </p>
            </article>

            <article class="app-panel about-page-history-card">
                <span class="material-icons about-page-pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">school</span>
                <h3>Expanded LMS Scope</h3>
                <p>
                    As the platform matured, it expanded beyond grading into a broader learning management system with lessons, quizzes, classroom tools, attendance workflows, and academic support content.
                </p>
            </article>

            <article class="app-panel about-page-history-card">
                <span class="material-icons about-page-pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">account_balance</span>
                <h3>HelloUniversity</h3>
                <p>
                    The rebrand to <strong>HelloUniversity</strong> reflects that wider scope: not just grade reporting, but a fuller academic platform built around learning, classroom operations, and institutional support.
                </p>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>

